#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:194
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Konqueror makes working with and managing your files easy. You can browse "
"both local and networked folders while enjoying advanced features such as "
"the powerful sidebar and file previews."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:198
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Konqueror is also a full featured and easy to use web browser which you can "
"use to explore the Internet. Enter the address (e.g. <a href=\"http://www."
"kde.org\">http://www.kde.org</a>) of a web page you would like to visit in "
"the location bar and press Enter, or choose an entry from the Bookmarks menu."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:203
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To return to the previous location, press the back button <img width='16' "
"height='16' src=\"%1\"></img> in the toolbar. "
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:206
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To quickly go to your Home folder press the home button <img width='16' "
"height='16' src=\"%1\"></img>."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:208
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"For more detailed documentation on Konqueror click <a href=\"%1\">here</a>."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:211
#, kde-format
msgid "Next: Tips & Tricks"
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:248
#, kde-format
msgid "Tips & Tricks"
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:249
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Use Web-Shortcuts: by typing \"gg: KDE\" one can search the Internet, using "
"Google, for the search phrase \"KDE\". There are a lot of Web-Shortcuts "
"predefined to make searching for software or looking up certain words in an "
"encyclopedia a breeze. You can even <a href=\"%1\">create your own</a> Web-"
"Shortcuts."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:254
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When you want to paste a new address into the Location toolbar you might "
"want to clear the current entry by pressing the black arrow with the white "
"cross <img width='16' height='16' src=\"%1\"></img> in the toolbar."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:258
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To create a link on your desktop pointing to the current page, simply drag "
"the icon (favicon) that is to the left of the Location toolbar, drop it on "
"to the desktop, and choose \"Icon\"."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:261
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can also find <img width='16' height='16' src=\"%1\" /> \"Full-Screen "
"Mode\" in the Settings menu. This feature is very useful for \"Talk\" "
"sessions."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:264
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Divide et impera (lat. \"Divide and conquer\") - by splitting a window into "
"two parts (e.g. Window -> <img width='16' height='16' src=\"%1\" /> Split "
"View Left/Right) you can make Konqueror appear the way you like."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:267
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Use the <a href=\"%1\">user-agent</a> feature if the website you are "
"visiting asks you to use a different browser (and do not forget to send a "
"complaint to the webmaster!)"
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:270
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The <img width='16' height='16' src=\"%1\"></img> History in your Sidebar "
"ensures that you can keep track of the pages you have visited recently."
msgstr ""

#: src/about/konq_aboutpage.cpp:272
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Advanced users will appreciate the Konsole which you can embed into "
"Konqueror (Settings -> <img width='16' height='16' SRC=\"%1\"></img> Show "
"Terminal Emulator)."
msgstr ""

